Background

		Mr. David F. Brussard has been Non-Executive Chairman of Safety Insurance Group, Inc. since March 2004 and has been its Director since October 2001. Mr. Brussard has significant experience with the insurance industry. He served as the Chief Executive officer and President of Safety Insurance Group, Inc. from June 2001 to March 31, 2016. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Safety Indemnity Insurance Company and Safety Insurance Company, subsidiaries ... of Safety Insurance Group Inc. from January 1999 to March 31, 2016. He served as Executive Vice President of the Insurance Subsidiaries from 1985 to 1999 and as Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer of the Insurance Subsidiaries from 1979 to 1999. He served as a Director of Safety Insurance Company. He is on the Board of Trustees of the Insurance Library Association of Boston.Read Full Background




